<TEXT>
<P>
Regarding "Backstage at 'Jeopardy!' " (by Patricia Ward Biederman, Jan. 29): I 
was a one-time champion on "Jeopardy!" last March, winning $12,801, a 
consolation-prize armoire and color TV, and a headful of golden memories. 
People ask me all the time what the experience was like, and rather than talk 
myself hoarse, I may just lend them your article, because you really captured 
it beautifully. 
</P>
<P>
LESLIE GOODMAN-MALAMUTH 
</P>
<P>
Washington, D.C. 
</P>
