Photo, Victoria Falls visitor seems oblivious to 400-foot drop at her feet. ; 
Photo, COLOR, An impressive amount of water spills over the lip of Victoria 
Falls, Zimbabwe Forest, river and waterfall are much as they always have been, 
without even guardrails to protect the unwary from the rocks below. ; Photo, 
