</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
AIKMAN, TROY; ATHLETIC TRAINING; DALLAS COWBOYS (FOOTBALL TEAM); FOOTBALL 
PLAYERS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
