BASKETBALL CHAMPIONSHIPS; HIGH SCHOOL ATHLETICS -- WOMEN 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA031989-0158 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 32922 </DOCID>
