after missing a free throw with two seconds left to play Saturday. DAVID 
MURONAKA / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Trabuco Hills' Rick Swanwick bumps Central 
Valley's Ron Golden while scoring. CHRISTINE WALTER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
