<TEXT>
<P>
Heartfelt congratulations to retiring editor Dick Turpin and his successor, 
Dick Barnes. Mr. Turpin's retirement plans, which include travel and the 
"enjoyment of time," refer to a possible book based on his rough-and-ready 
experiences, which I surely hope will materialize. 
</P>
