<P>
NEW COUNTRY SIDE INN PLANNED IN YORBA LINDA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A $9-million, 107-suite Country Side Inn will open early next year at Savi 
Ranch Business Park, Yorba Linda. It will be the fifth Southland Country Side 
Inn. 
</P>
<P>
Ayres Construction, Newport Beach, purchased the site from Savi Ranch 
Associates, Newport Beach, for $1.1 million. Coldwell Banker Commercial Real 
Estate Services represented both parties. 
</P>
